The paper discusses privacy risks associated with online activities and proposes methods for preserving privacy while maintaining the utility of the data for classification tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computer security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Among these, cs.CR is the most likely category as the paper primarily focuses on privacy risks and preserving anonymity.
